---
---
<header class="min-h-[calc(100vh-96px)] flex items-center justify-center relative py-16 sm:py-0">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.04),transparent_55%),radial-gradient(900px_600px_at_30%_15%,rgba(0,0,0,0.06),transparent_60%)]"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black/40 to-transparent"></div>

  <img
    src="/pins/talazbragoles-pins-1.png"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="hidden sm:block absolute -left-24 top-24 w-[520px] rotate-[-6deg] opacity-[0.12] grayscale contrast-[2.6] brightness-[0.35] mix-blend-multiply blur-[0.2px]"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <img
    src="/pins/talazbragoles-pins-2.png"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="hidden sm:block absolute -right-24 bottom-10 w-[520px] rotate-[5deg] opacity-[0.12] grayscale contrast-[2.6] brightness-[0.35] mix-blend-multiply blur-[0.2px]"
    loading="lazy"
  />

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-5">
      <div class="text-[0.7rem] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-black/70 border border-black/20 bg-white/60 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
        Fanzine–Archivo · Edición viva
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="mt-7 text-[clamp(3.1rem,10vw,8rem)] font-black tracking-[0.22em] uppercase leading-[0.95] text-black drop-shadow-[0_1px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] break-words">
      TALAZBRÁGOLES
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-4 text-black/80 text-[clamp(1rem,3.4vw,2.05rem)] font-bold tracking-[0.28em] uppercase">
      JORNADAS DE ROL Y SIMULACIÓN
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 sm:mt-14 text-[clamp(1.25rem,4.6vw,3.2rem)] font-light text-black/85 leading-tight max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      «Que lo unido por la fantasía<br />no sea roto por la realidad.»
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 inline-flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-3xl border border-black/20 bg-white/55 px-7 py-5">
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-black/70">¿Qué encontrarás aquí?</div>
      <div class="text-black/80 text-sm sm:text-base">
        Un <span class="font-semibold">archivo vivo</span>: recuerdos, fuentes y una línea temporal que solo crece cuando hay documentación.
      </div>
    </div>

    <a
      href="#historia"
      class="mt-12 sm:mt-20 inline-flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 px-8 sm:px-14 py-5 sm:py-6 bg-black text-white font-black text-lg sm:text-2xl rounded-2xl shadow-[0_10px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.16)] active:translate-y-1 transition-all focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[color:var(--accent)] focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[color:var(--paper)]"
    >
      ABRIR EL DOSSIER
      <span class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-none" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="absolute bottom-6 sm:bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[0.65rem] sm:text-xs text-black/60 tracking-[0.26em] font-semibold text-center px-6 uppercase">
    Hecho para recordar · Hecho para documentar
  </p>
</header>
